/>\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d907f0d8007f4d25cfdc811b6f1a62e74a60fbec","tid":1508173,"uid":275873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06cb1ba944043cd737220a541b0d79d80b17e8c8","tid":1508173,"uid":190858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"[核彈文宣]828#ProtestToo集會全世界都要去 平權=反極權 將火源燒開去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"到時見!"},{"pid":"646240646b04c74392f0b2a8ef69b34b8db6f391","tid":1508173,"uid":275873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ef0b68c0671565f5166cbeefd8103fba6adae4f","tid":1508173,"uid":312014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:42:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"蛋奶應該補充到"},{"pid":"e45b73c982996b8f28f88c953bb6cbdc17ab1682","tid":1508173,"uid":275873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd2b925df6b18dfbc595fcff99b9bbc601a5e10","tid":1508173,"uid":307047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"有蛋奶素有純素<br />\n盡咗小小力tick咗畀你<br />\n希望無漏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">素</span></strong>球&middot;缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SixJwq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSixJwq2.jpg&h=a5b6213e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rX5SpL2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrX5SpL2.jpg&h=69e7fc96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3iwFjo.jpg\" data-t